1
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,280
I let him back into my life,

2
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,440
so I have to accept the hurt.

3
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:47,840
It's not wrong to trust someone…

4
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,600
…especially someone you love.

5
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,440
<i>Let's try taking a break</i>

6
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:55,920
<i>from this relationship</i>
<i>and go deal with our own problems.</i>

7
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,440
So that means we're only going
to love each other

8
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,600
when we're happy?

9
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:04,760
I would like to take responsibility
by resigning as a company director,

10
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,200
effective today.

11
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,920
<i>Actually, I didn't sell them.</i>

12
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,920
I gave them to him.

13
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,880
What if Mr. Rachen doesn't give them back?

14
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,560
Someone with dirty hands like that

15
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,200
has to leave some kind of trace.

16
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:16,520
Can you find evidence that Mrs. Mookmanee

17
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,720
has done something illegal?

18
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,680
Why don't you let him prove himself

19
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,560
and see if he only wants money or not?

20
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,840
Call your daughter over here,
and I'll transfer it.

21
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:28,600
Dad?

22
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,720
Thank you, Mr. Trai.

23
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:28,080
Feels good, right?

24
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,400
Having me here.

25
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,400
Let's stay like this
for five more minutes.

26
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:09,400
I have to send my presentation to Petch.

27
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:29,520
Work, work. I have to send my work.

28
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,560
Where were you last night?

29
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,240
She stayed at my place.

30
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,280
But nothing happened.

31
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,400
Where's Dad?

32
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,800
You told Dad to go back
to that house, right?

33
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:47,160
Kanah.

34
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,000
How…

35
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,560
did you know?

36
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,040
I heard you.

37
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:56,040
You told Dad to go get evidence
from Mrs. Mookmanee's house.

38
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:02,080
Mrs. Mookmanee

39
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,680
has been so cruel to me.

40
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:05,000
If she gets arrested,

41
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:07,320
I'd be so happy.

42
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,200
So,

43
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:12,560
can you find evidence that Mrs. Mookmanee
has done something illegal?

44
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,800
Anything… stock fraud, any fraud at all.

45
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,320
Can you help find it for me?

46
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:19,160
I can't do that. I got thrown out.

47
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,680
I can't go back.

48
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,600
You're such a good actor.

49
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,040
Something this simple

50
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:26,040
is not beyond your ability.

51
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:30,520
What the hell were you thinking
sending Dad to risk his life like that?

52
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,200
- I--
- I know you want to help Mr. Trai.

53
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,520
You want Mrs. Mookmanee to get arrested.

54
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:38,320
But weren't you worried
about Dad's safety?

55
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:40,480
Mrs. Mookmanee is ruthless.

56
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:42,600
What if he got caught?

57
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,120
What if he got hurt?

58
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,440
What if he got killed?

59
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:48,160
Weren't you worried about him at all?

60
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:51,920
Dad's been trying to change,

61
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:54,080
trying to be a better father.

62
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:56,360
You're the only one
who has never opened your heart.

63
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:58,400
How long are you going to pressure him?!

64
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,760
Does he have
to prove himself with his life?

65
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,080
Kanah, let's calm down.

66
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,320
Pakbung has her reasons.

67
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:05,000
Then say them!

68
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:08,200
I'm standing right here!

69
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,400
You always keep everything to yourself!

70
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:12,400
You think that's cool?!

71
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:15,920
You are

72
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,640
so damn selfish.

73
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,880
Kanah.

74
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,040
Let me handle it.

75
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,240
Hold on.

76
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,720
You really want to know the reason?

77
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,520
If Pakbung won't tell you, I will.

78
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:19,640
I'm fine.

79
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,520
Hold it. You might need it
after you hear this.

80
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,960
Dad really went back to gambling?

81
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:50,040
It's true that Mr. Yongyut
went back to gambling.

82
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,240
But what Pakbung did

83
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:53,960
was too risky.

84
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:56,160
What you said earlier wasn't wrong.

85
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,400
But I want you to know that

86
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:05,760
last night,

87
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,880
Pakbung cried herself to sleep.

88
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:12,040
Your sister is hurting a lot.

89
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:14,000
Why didn't she tell me?

90
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:20,320
Maybe she didn't want to see the look
on your face that I'm seeing now.

91
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:22,440
I'm going to talk to her.

92
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,360
I'll be the one leaving.

93
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,640
Bung…

94
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:49,760
Talk nicely to each other.

95
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:51,480
Go.

96
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:05,480
I saw how happy you were having Dad back.

97
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:08,640
I didn't want to disappoint you.

98
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,480
But what I did

99
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,360
was terrible.

100
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,480
I really was careless.

101
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:17,000
I didn't think he'd really go.

102
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,080
I'm sorry.

103
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,760
You're so small.

104
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,920
Why do you try to carry everything alone?

105
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,720
If Dad went back to gambling,

106
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,240
just tell me.

107
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,000
If you're hurting,

108
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,120
just tell me.

109
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:39,240
Let me take care of you too.

110
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,760
Let me stand beside you

111
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:45,160
when you have problems for once, Bung.

112
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:49,120
Don't keep everything to yourself anymore.

113
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:05,200
Why did you keep everything to yourself?

114
00:11:05,280 --> 00:11:07,960
Why didn't you tell me?

115
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:19,280
Kanah…

116
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:32,360
Here.

117
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:36,480
Thank you.

118
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:51,560
I have something for you.

119
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,320
Wow.

120
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,080
Five stars?

121
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,160
Too many? I can take them back.

122
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,840
No. They're mine now.

123
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:16,600
I've got five stars.

124
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,760
Any reward?

125
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:25,040
You already got it.

126
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,840
This milk tea?

127
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:33,840
Yes.

128
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:35,280
Finish it.

129
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,240
It's over 100 baht.

130
00:12:47,800 --> 00:12:49,040
Do you think

131
00:12:49,760 --> 00:12:50,840
what Kanah said

132
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:52,040
could really happen?

133
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:54,760
If Dad got caught by Mrs. Mookmanee…

134
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,920
Right now, your dad is safe.

135
00:12:58,640 --> 00:12:59,640
There's nothing to worry about.

136
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,440
How do you know?

137
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,560
I have a whispering spirit.

138
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:10,240
Thank you.

139
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:15,040
Thank you for being here.

140
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:33,000
I can't trace Mrs. Mookmanee's nominees.

141
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:35,040
I think

142
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,560
she must've cleaned everything up.

143
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:38,680
Finding proof

144
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:40,080
of her doing illegal things

145
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:42,160
is even harder

146
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:44,120
unless we get some clues
from someone close to her.

147
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,160
The only one from her circle we have

148
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:47,160
is Mr. Yongyut.

149
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,800
Right now, he's in custody.

150
00:13:48,880 --> 00:13:50,560
I see Mrs. Mookmanee's people

151
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:51,840
keep checking on him.

152
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:54,440
- Keep watching him.
- Yes, sir.

153
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:57,040
There's one more person
who knows everything.

154
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:58,240
But I think

155
00:13:58,880 --> 00:14:01,040
buying him might be
even harder than Mr. Yongyut.

156
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:05,200
If you mean Mrs. Mookmanee's secretary…

157
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,000
I already have a plan.

158
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,840
We want your cooperation.

159
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:20,880
This is only the first payment.

160
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:24,240
If you bring us proof
of Mrs. Mookmanee's crimes,

161
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,960
we'll reward you

162
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:27,680
as much as you want.

163
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:34,040
I won't take your offer.

164
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:35,800
Please leave.

165
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:37,960
How old is your child now?

166
00:14:55,760 --> 00:14:58,440
How many days have you not gone home
and hugged your child

167
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:00,080
because of that bruise on your face?

168
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:05,880
Maybe you're afraid your child
will be disappointed or you're ashamed.

169
00:15:06,560 --> 00:15:08,280
But I'm sure your child

170
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:10,040
will never truly be happy

171
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:13,080
if she finds out what you had to do

172
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:15,200
to earn the money that raised her.

173
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:18,240
You don't need to speak for my family.

174
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:20,760
My father once chose
money and work over me.

175
00:15:21,280 --> 00:15:23,920
You know what that did to us.

176
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:27,440
I resented him. I was never proud of him.

177
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:30,120
Do you want your child
to feel that way about you?

178
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:36,720
Your child's future

179
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:39,680
doesn't depend
on how much money you provide.

180
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,160
It depends on this,

181
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:44,680
your love for her.

182
00:15:44,760 --> 00:15:46,400
I just want to help.

183
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:49,600
I want you to be able
to face your child with dignity.

184
00:16:08,920 --> 00:16:09,880
Money

185
00:16:11,280 --> 00:16:12,840
is the only dignity that matters.

186
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:16,240
Please leave.

187
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:19,080
No matter what,

188
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:22,800
I will never betray Mrs. Mookmanee.

189
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:45,360
You said you had a plan.

190
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,840
I expected something better.

191
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:49,840
Lee and Prarop found something out.

192
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:51,760
The secretary

193
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:53,320
loves his daughter more than anything.

194
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:55,120
He tolerates everything

195
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,480
Mrs. Mookmanee does

196
00:16:56,560 --> 00:16:58,840
because he needs money for his family.

197
00:17:00,040 --> 00:17:02,120
If he's endured all this for money,

198
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:05,040
he won't change his mind
because you appealed to his idea of love.

199
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:06,680
Well, well.

200
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:08,599
Aren't we on good terms now

201
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:09,960
because of love?

202
00:17:17,079 --> 00:17:18,760
If you don't think it'll work,

203
00:17:18,839 --> 00:17:19,720
then wait.

204
00:17:20,599 --> 00:17:21,440
Wait for what?

205
00:17:21,520 --> 00:17:24,160
Oh, Mr. Chairman.

206
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:26,640
We've cast the line.

207
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:28,680
Small fish, big fish,
we're bound to catch something.

208
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:34,800
Let's go.

209
00:17:58,440 --> 00:18:01,560
This morning, Trai and Rachen
went to see your secretary.

210
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:03,560
Using Mr. Yongyut failed,

211
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:05,760
so now they're targeting my people?

212
00:18:06,360 --> 00:18:08,400
Can your secretary be trusted?

213
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:16,080
No one would ever betray my money.

214
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:20,000
And what if Trai
didn't use money to lure him?

215
00:18:32,800 --> 00:18:34,320
<i>Your child's future</i>

216
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:37,160
<i>doesn't depend</i>
<i>on how much money you provide.</i>

217
00:18:37,240 --> 00:18:38,960
It depends on this,

218
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:41,920
your love for her.

219
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:45,560
I want you to be able
to face your child with dignity.

220
00:18:57,720 --> 00:19:00,880
Can you really protect me
and my family from Mrs. Mook?

221
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:24,960
Go!

222
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:32,520
He really kept evidence here.

223
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:39,320
After all these years,

224
00:19:39,400 --> 00:19:42,040
don't you know
that I hate traitors the most?

225
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:45,560
I'm sorry.

226
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:48,000
I'm sorry. It's my fault.

227
00:19:48,080 --> 00:19:49,280
Please forgive me.

228
00:19:49,360 --> 00:19:51,240
Please don't hurt me.

229
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:58,280
Just borrow Yongyut's story.

230
00:19:58,880 --> 00:19:59,720
Gambling.

231
00:19:59,800 --> 00:20:00,920
Debts.

232
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:04,120
Too ashamed to face your family.

233
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:06,040
I'll write the suicide note for you.

234
00:20:10,360 --> 00:20:11,520
- No!
- Come here!

235
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:13,560
- Let me go!
- Come here!

236
00:20:14,760 --> 00:20:15,840
- Come here!
- No!

237
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:18,080
What are you doing? Please, no!

238
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:21,640
You're just killing yourself.

239
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:23,760
No.

240
00:20:24,440 --> 00:20:25,600
Please, no.

241
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,320
Bring me the hard drive.

242
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:04,720
I'll destroy it myself.

243
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:46,600
Why do you look

244
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:48,320
so happy today?

245
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:50,720
We're going to make merit.

246
00:21:50,800 --> 00:21:52,920
You know I love making merit.

247
00:21:53,520 --> 00:21:57,120
It helps purify the soul.

248
00:22:10,600 --> 00:22:11,520
What is it?

249
00:22:14,760 --> 00:22:16,680
<i>Footage from a hidden camera</i>

250
00:22:16,760 --> 00:22:19,200
<i>clearly shows the moment of the attack.</i>

251
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:23,440
Looks like your secretary
installed a hidden camera.

252
00:22:23,520 --> 00:22:26,080
It recorded both video and audio
of the moment you killed him.

253
00:22:31,520 --> 00:22:32,600
Mrs. Mookmanee,

254
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:34,520
the police are here again.

255
00:22:49,280 --> 00:22:50,880
Mrs. Mookmanee Chaiyarattanawong,

256
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:53,680
I'm here to read your arrest warrant

257
00:22:53,760 --> 00:22:55,160
for attempted murder.

258
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:56,840
Wait. Attempted murder?

259
00:22:56,920 --> 00:22:58,880
Where's the proof?

260
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:00,600
Or is it because of that video clip?

261
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:02,320
It's obviously fake.

262
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:04,320
It was edited to frame my mom.

263
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:07,240
You can't issue a warrant
based on a short video like that.

264
00:23:07,320 --> 00:23:09,760
What if there's a witness
to confirm it in person?

265
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:20,640
Impossible.

266
00:23:22,120 --> 00:23:23,120
You were dead.

267
00:23:38,160 --> 00:23:40,000
His heart's still beating,
but his pulse is very weak.

268
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:45,200
Hello, emergency rescue?

269
00:23:46,080 --> 00:23:47,160
Someone attempted suicide.

270
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:49,000
He slit his wrist with a knife.

271
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:50,520
There's a lot of blood.

272
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:51,640
Please hurry.

273
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:52,640
We're at a condo.

274
00:23:54,520 --> 00:23:56,200
At first, he almost didn't make it.

275
00:23:56,280 --> 00:23:59,040
But it seems your secretary
loves you very much, Mrs. Mookmanee.

276
00:23:59,120 --> 00:24:01,160
That's why he refused
to leave you so easily.

277
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:06,720
Mrs. Mookmanee,

278
00:24:07,760 --> 00:24:09,320
you meant to kill me.

279
00:24:10,280 --> 00:24:11,680
How could you do this to me?

280
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:13,240
Mrs. Mookmanee,

281
00:24:13,320 --> 00:24:15,360
please come with us
to give a statement at the station.

282
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:16,840
Don't you know who I am?

283
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:17,800
- Excuse me.
- Huh?

284
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:18,720
- Get away.
- Mom.

285
00:24:18,800 --> 00:24:19,720
Don't touch me.

286
00:24:19,800 --> 00:24:20,840
- Please cooperate.
- Let go!

287
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:22,720
- I said let go!
- Please cooperate.

288
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:25,440
Do you all want to be transferred out?
Let go of my mom. Let go.

289
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:26,640
- Let my mom go!
- Ma'am!

290
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:28,200
- Let go!
- Please cooperate.

291
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:29,880
Then take both of them in,

292
00:24:29,960 --> 00:24:32,200
for obstruction of official duties.

293
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:34,520
Don't involve my daughter.

294
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:36,240
She has nothing to do with this.

295
00:24:37,080 --> 00:24:38,240
Take Mika away.

296
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:41,520
Let go! Don't touch me.
I'm going to help my mom!

297
00:24:41,600 --> 00:24:43,160
- Mom! Mom!
- Mika, stop.

298
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,480
Don't make a scene.

299
00:24:45,440 --> 00:24:46,520
I will be fine.

300
00:24:48,080 --> 00:24:49,880
This won't be enough to bring me down.

301
00:24:51,280 --> 00:24:52,480
Who said this was all?

302
00:24:55,120 --> 00:24:56,000
Excuse me.

303
00:24:56,080 --> 00:24:57,240
Mom!

304
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,040
This way, please.

305
00:25:08,560 --> 00:25:09,680
Mom.

306
00:25:24,320 --> 00:25:26,840
<i>The DSI is preparing to press charges</i>
<i>against Mrs. Mookmanee Chaiyarattanawong,</i>

307
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:28,920
<i>heiress to a well-known banking family,</i>

308
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:30,320
<i>for concealing shareholdings.</i>

309
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:32,400
<i>Police also have clear evidence</i>

310
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:34,840
<i>linking her to corruption</i>

311
00:25:34,920 --> 00:25:37,200
<i>and bribery of several politicians</i>

312
00:25:37,280 --> 00:25:39,400
<i>as well as attempted murder.</i>

313
00:25:40,760 --> 00:25:41,760
This time,

314
00:25:42,360 --> 00:25:44,320
she's definitely checking in
to prison for the long haul.

315
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:45,280
Yeah.

316
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:48,760
Oh, wait.

317
00:25:48,840 --> 00:25:52,080
Didn't Mr. Lee say
Mrs. Mookmanee destroyed all the evidence?

318
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:53,960
So where did Mr. Trai get it from?

319
00:25:55,360 --> 00:25:56,880
You're not updated.

320
00:25:56,960 --> 00:25:58,560
Mr. Prarop told me

321
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:01,280
the secretary backed everything up.

322
00:26:01,360 --> 00:26:03,360
After he recovered,
he gave it all to Mr. Trai.

323
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,640
Hold on.

324
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:06,400
Are you flexing on me?

325
00:26:06,480 --> 00:26:07,320
Flexing what?

326
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:09,840
Flexing that your guy is better?

327
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:12,160
That you talk more often
and get more updates than I do?

328
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:15,520
Mr. Prarop is not my guy.
We're just friends.

329
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:16,640
No, you just said--

330
00:26:16,720 --> 00:26:18,400
- Because you--
- Ugh!

331
00:26:19,080 --> 00:26:19,920
Enough.

332
00:26:20,440 --> 00:26:21,520
In conclusion,

333
00:26:21,600 --> 00:26:23,640
my man is the best.

334
00:26:26,120 --> 00:26:27,200
Mr. Trai

335
00:26:27,280 --> 00:26:29,520
handled Mookmanee perfectly.

336
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:31,560
- Sure.
- Sure.

337
00:26:36,160 --> 00:26:38,760
Kanah, aren't you going to say anything?

338
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:40,440
Mrs. Mookmanee got arrested.

339
00:26:42,040 --> 00:26:42,880
Kanah.

340
00:26:43,480 --> 00:26:44,880
Did he hear us?

341
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,800
Kanah!

342
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:49,320
Huh? What did you say?

343
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:54,680
Is he okay?

344
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:09,040
What are you doing?

345
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:11,400
Why haven't you gotten me out yet?

346
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:13,560
It's not that simple.

347
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:16,280
The police are opposing your bail.

348
00:27:16,360 --> 00:27:17,440
Why?

349
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:20,680
Did you call the Deputy Minister?

350
00:27:20,760 --> 00:27:22,080
He's not answering.

351
00:27:24,600 --> 00:27:25,840
Then give me the phone.

352
00:27:27,120 --> 00:27:28,080
I'll call him myself.

353
00:27:30,040 --> 00:27:33,120
Give me the phone. I'll call the Minister.

354
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:35,560
The police now have evidence

355
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:38,280
of bribery

356
00:27:38,360 --> 00:27:41,320
and corruption involving
several officials and ministers.

357
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:43,840
No one is going to want to take your call.

358
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:52,000
Damn it!

359
00:27:52,080 --> 00:27:54,960
I won't let this end so easily, Trai!

360
00:28:03,560 --> 00:28:05,760
MR. AEK CHAIYA
10 MILLION BAHT

361
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:09,600
I know it's not much,

362
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:12,240
but it should be enough for you
to start over.

363
00:28:13,240 --> 00:28:14,800
Thank you so much.

364
00:28:16,880 --> 00:28:18,080
Wait.

365
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:19,800
What's going on?

366
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:21,560
When did you make this deal?

367
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:24,520
And why did you agree to be the bait?

368
00:28:25,600 --> 00:28:27,640
I never meant to use him as bait.

369
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:31,160
I didn't expect
Mrs. Mookmanee to hurt him either.

370
00:28:31,760 --> 00:28:33,560
Well, Mr. Rachen.

371
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:36,600
When you and Mr. Trai visited him,

372
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:37,920
I was there too.

373
00:28:38,480 --> 00:28:41,200
I saw Rut tailing Mr. Trai.

374
00:28:50,760 --> 00:28:52,720
<i>And I saw Rut taking photos.</i>

375
00:28:53,480 --> 00:28:55,760
<i>I knew he'd report it to Mrs. Mookmanee.</i>

376
00:28:56,800 --> 00:28:59,160
So Mr. Trai told Lee and me to keep watch.

377
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:03,160
When we saw Mrs. Mookmanee arrive,
we immediately called Mr. Trai.

378
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:08,120
So, that's how you saved me in time.

379
00:29:08,960 --> 00:29:10,120
Thank you.

380
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:11,840
Actually…

381
00:29:12,760 --> 00:29:14,120
I almost got you killed.

382
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:16,200
No.

383
00:29:18,760 --> 00:29:20,440
Working for someone like her…

384
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:23,400
even if I hadn't died that day,

385
00:29:24,280 --> 00:29:26,320
it would've happened eventually.

386
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:27,880
That's why

387
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:30,800
I hid a camera in the room,

388
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:33,480
so if anything happened,

389
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:36,960
people would know who did it.

390
00:29:52,360 --> 00:29:54,840
I always wanted to resign,

391
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:59,120
but I didn't have

392
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:01,680
the courage.

393
00:30:02,320 --> 00:30:04,760
Thank you so much

394
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:07,440
for freeing me from her.

395
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:26,400
What's wrong?

396
00:30:29,920 --> 00:30:33,880
Didn't you say we should talk
if something's bugging us?

397
00:30:33,960 --> 00:30:34,800
Then talk.

398
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:36,960
Well…

399
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:42,160
I miss Dad.

400
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:46,080
But it's not like
I want him back or anything.

401
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:47,320
- Just--
- You're worried about him.

402
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:48,720
Mm.

403
00:30:50,080 --> 00:30:52,080
I can't help thinking.

404
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:53,680
Now that Mrs. Mookmanee has been arrested,

405
00:30:53,760 --> 00:30:55,320
what's going to happen to him?

406
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:56,680
What is he doing? Where is he?

407
00:30:56,760 --> 00:30:59,120
If we at least knew he was okay,

408
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:00,720
I'd feel better.

409
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:05,320
Bung,

410
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:07,000
you told me to say it.

411
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:08,680
You can't get mad at me.

412
00:31:08,760 --> 00:31:10,280
Yeah.

413
00:31:10,360 --> 00:31:11,600
I'm not mad.

414
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:16,440
I also want to know…

415
00:31:18,120 --> 00:31:19,160
how he's doing.

416
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:41,200
I have to…

417
00:31:41,760 --> 00:31:42,960
thank you,

418
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:43,880
Mr. Trai,

419
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:46,800
for bailing me out again.

420
00:31:49,560 --> 00:31:51,680
This time, I was the one who reported you.

421
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:57,120
You failed Mrs. Mookmanee.

422
00:31:57,200 --> 00:31:58,400
She wouldn't have let you live,

423
00:31:59,280 --> 00:32:01,000
so I put you somewhere safe.

424
00:32:01,080 --> 00:32:03,000
Now that she's been arrested,

425
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:04,360
I bailed you out.

426
00:32:08,760 --> 00:32:10,640
why would you be worried about me?

427
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,040
I'm not worried about you.

428
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:14,680
I'm worried about Pakbung.

429
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:17,920
Pakbung saw it.

430
00:32:18,520 --> 00:32:21,040
She saw that you lured her there
so Mrs. Mookmanee's men could hurt her.

431
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:25,920
I…

432
00:32:29,320 --> 00:32:31,240
I didn't want to do it.

433
00:32:31,760 --> 00:32:33,320
I didn't mean to.

434
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:36,360
Mrs. Mook was going to kill me.

435
00:32:37,080 --> 00:32:39,160
Rut had a gun to me. I had no choice.

436
00:32:39,240 --> 00:32:40,440
You did have a choice.

437
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:43,480
You chose this path yourself.

438
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:48,600
I've taken the wrong path before too,

439
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:50,600
so I have no right to judge you.

440
00:32:51,800 --> 00:32:53,160
But like I said,

441
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:56,000
if you still want to keep your family,

442
00:32:56,080 --> 00:32:58,680
please love them
more than yourself for once.

443
00:33:15,440 --> 00:33:18,000
Have dinner without me, okay?

444
00:33:18,840 --> 00:33:20,760
I'm helping Mr. Trai
at the school tonight.

445
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:23,320
I'll be back late.

446
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:26,120
I know.

447
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:28,120
I'm not staying over.

448
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:32,040
Oh? Kanah,

449
00:33:32,680 --> 00:33:33,760
I gotta go now.

450
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:47,400
You fell asleep waiting for me?

451
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:55,880
I'm not even that late.

452
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:09,120
You must be exhausted.

453
00:34:37,639 --> 00:34:39,239
My good boy.

454
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:47,920
You're the best.

455
00:34:55,719 --> 00:34:57,800
Try doing it while I'm not asleep.

456
00:35:05,720 --> 00:35:06,760
What did you do to me?

457
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:07,920
Nothing.

458
00:35:11,160 --> 00:35:13,440
There are CCTV cameras
all over the school.

459
00:35:14,080 --> 00:35:15,200
There's one right there.

460
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:20,520
Then go check the footage yourself.

461
00:35:20,600 --> 00:35:21,960
No.

462
00:35:22,520 --> 00:35:23,640
I want to see it right here.

463
00:35:24,600 --> 00:35:25,440
Right now.

464
00:35:26,800 --> 00:35:29,360
I just put a sticker

465
00:35:29,440 --> 00:35:31,040
on your forehead.

466
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:35,640
That's not it.

467
00:35:37,560 --> 00:35:38,760
I felt…

468
00:35:40,480 --> 00:35:41,960
your breath.

469
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:57,160
My good boy.

470
00:35:58,240 --> 00:36:00,160
You're the best.

471
00:36:35,120 --> 00:36:36,800
I don't know if it's just me…

472
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:39,640
but the stars
look especially beautiful tonight.

473
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:43,800
That's because
you took down Mrs. Mookmanee.

474
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:47,440
You're happy,

475
00:36:47,520 --> 00:36:50,040
so everything looks beautiful.

476
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:52,120
See? I told you.

477
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:53,280
Your life

478
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:56,360
runs on revenge too.

479
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:58,960
The reason I feel better…

480
00:37:00,800 --> 00:37:02,800
is because you're here with me.

481
00:37:06,040 --> 00:37:07,360
Come here. Let me hug you.

482
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:13,280
Hey.

483
00:37:14,080 --> 00:37:15,280
What are you doing?

484
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:17,760
Behave yourself.

485
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:19,440
Your mom's watching from up there, see?

486
00:37:19,520 --> 00:37:22,800
My mom is kind. She wouldn't mind.

487
00:37:25,640 --> 00:37:29,320
Your mom might be kind,
but your dad isn't that kind.

488
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:33,040
He doesn't really like me.

489
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:35,760
If my parents see me happy,

490
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:37,120
they'll be happy too.

491
00:37:42,040 --> 00:37:43,520
Should we show them our love?

492
00:37:43,600 --> 00:37:44,640
What?

493
00:37:46,520 --> 00:37:48,200
I'm going home. Kanah's waiting.

494
00:37:48,280 --> 00:37:50,240
No. You can't go.

495
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:52,400
Kanah's waiting.

496
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:53,560
I won't let you go.

497
00:37:54,160 --> 00:37:56,000
Alright, alright.

498
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:57,680
Come on. Let's go home.

499
00:37:58,360 --> 00:37:59,240
Come on.

500
00:38:03,520 --> 00:38:04,480
What are you smiling at?

501
00:38:05,640 --> 00:38:07,280
You reached out your hand first.

502
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:13,320
I'm sorry.

503
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:15,280
Well…

504
00:38:19,320 --> 00:38:20,320
I…

505
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:22,840
You're not ready yet.

506
00:38:23,520 --> 00:38:24,960
You're a good man,

507
00:38:25,040 --> 00:38:27,480
an incredibly good man.

508
00:38:27,560 --> 00:38:30,360
But whenever I try to move forward,

509
00:38:32,560 --> 00:38:33,920
I get scared…

510
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:36,960
scared it'll be like with my father.

511
00:38:40,040 --> 00:38:41,920
But it's not your fault.

512
00:38:42,520 --> 00:38:43,840
It's me.

513
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:48,680
I still can't get past that feeling.

514
00:38:57,320 --> 00:38:58,320
It's okay.

515
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:00,360
I understand.

516
00:39:03,720 --> 00:39:04,880
Go get your things.

517
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:08,040
I'll take you home.

518
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:09,840
Let's go.

519
00:39:20,200 --> 00:39:22,920
Did I make you so afraid of love?

520
00:39:27,560 --> 00:39:30,080
- Let me go. I said let go!
- Miss…

521
00:39:30,160 --> 00:39:31,720
I'm going to help my mom.

522
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:33,200
You can't.

523
00:39:33,280 --> 00:39:35,320
Mrs. Mook ordered
that you can't go outside.

524
00:39:35,400 --> 00:39:37,360
How can I just sit here? Let go.

525
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:38,840
Let go!

526
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:42,680
You can't help Mrs. Mookmanee.

527
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:45,360
If you go, you'll only make it worse.

528
00:39:45,440 --> 00:39:48,960
When the police came, where were you?
Why didn't you help her?

529
00:39:49,040 --> 00:39:50,040
Did you forget

530
00:39:50,120 --> 00:39:51,880
she got you out of prison?

531
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:53,480
How can you be so ungrateful?

532
00:39:56,680 --> 00:39:59,400
I was afraid if the police saw me here,

533
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:01,240
it would make things worse for her.

534
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:02,600
That's why I stepped away.

535
00:40:02,680 --> 00:40:04,960
I want to help her too.

536
00:40:05,040 --> 00:40:06,840
I want to repay her so badly.

537
00:40:06,920 --> 00:40:08,640
But what can someone like me do?

538
00:40:08,720 --> 00:40:10,840
I don't have power like you do, Ms. Mika.

539
00:40:23,480 --> 00:40:25,760
I heard

540
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:28,760
Trai wants to destroy Mrs. Mookmanee

541
00:40:28,840 --> 00:40:30,040
because of Pakbung.

542
00:40:34,520 --> 00:40:37,000
Right now, you're the only one

543
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:39,760
who can avenge your mother.

544
00:40:51,440 --> 00:40:52,480
This is

545
00:40:52,560 --> 00:40:53,400
your power.

546
00:41:08,640 --> 00:41:09,480
Slowly, Mom.

547
00:41:10,160 --> 00:41:11,760
Finally, I'm home.

548
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:13,760
I was in the hospital for so long.

549
00:41:13,840 --> 00:41:15,160
It was so boring.

550
00:41:19,160 --> 00:41:20,080
Mom…

551
00:41:27,640 --> 00:41:28,680
I'm sorry.

552
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:40,600
You fainted
and hit your head because of me.

553
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:43,480
I don't even want to think about…

554
00:41:44,520 --> 00:41:46,800
If it had been worse,

555
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:49,880
how…

556
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:54,280
how would I live?

557
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:01,560
I'm fine now.

558
00:42:01,640 --> 00:42:02,560
Alright?

559
00:42:02,640 --> 00:42:04,960
I was in the hospital for a few weeks.

560
00:42:05,040 --> 00:42:07,280
The doctors checked me every day.

561
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:08,200
Now

562
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:11,360
I'll be healthy for years.

563
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:23,960
I keep asking myself…

564
00:42:27,040 --> 00:42:29,640
what have I been doing all this time?

565
00:42:30,960 --> 00:42:32,680
Chasing men,

566
00:42:34,480 --> 00:42:36,440
chasing love,

567
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:38,440
dreams,

568
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:40,640
and money.

569
00:42:42,240 --> 00:42:44,800
I wanted what others have.

570
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:49,960
It was exhausting

571
00:42:50,040 --> 00:42:51,560
and wasted my time.

572
00:43:02,080 --> 00:43:03,840
And it made me

573
00:43:04,640 --> 00:43:08,640
forget the most important person
in my life.

574
00:43:19,240 --> 00:43:20,920
All this time,

575
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:23,000
you were just lost.

576
00:43:24,520 --> 00:43:26,360
But if you've realized it now,

577
00:43:26,920 --> 00:43:30,120
it's not too late to start over.

578
00:43:31,120 --> 00:43:32,960
I'll always support you.

579
00:43:34,080 --> 00:43:35,960
I love you.

580
00:43:37,320 --> 00:43:38,480
I love you very much.

581
00:43:41,640 --> 00:43:43,160
I love you, Mom.

582
00:43:45,320 --> 00:43:47,040
Don't cry, dear.

583
00:43:47,840 --> 00:43:49,040
Don't cry.

584
00:43:50,800 --> 00:43:53,520
Mom, wait a minute.
I'll go buy food for you.

585
00:44:05,440 --> 00:44:06,320
Rut.

586
00:44:07,360 --> 00:44:08,960
So you're trying to start a new life?

587
00:44:10,440 --> 00:44:11,680
What do you want?

588
00:44:11,760 --> 00:44:13,520
Why are you so scared?

589
00:44:13,600 --> 00:44:15,440
I'm not here to kill you or anything.

590
00:44:18,880 --> 00:44:21,040
Did Trai stop sending
bodyguards after you?

591
00:44:23,080 --> 00:44:24,280
I'm the one who told him…

592
00:44:25,920 --> 00:44:27,880
I don't need anyone protecting me anymore.

593
00:44:29,120 --> 00:44:30,440
If you hate me

594
00:44:31,040 --> 00:44:32,800
and want to do something to me, go ahead.

595
00:44:32,880 --> 00:44:34,000
I take full responsibility.

596
00:44:34,080 --> 00:44:36,160
Yes. It's your fault for lying to me!

597
00:44:37,160 --> 00:44:38,800
But I never once
thought about killing you.

598
00:44:39,720 --> 00:44:41,320
Then why won't you just let me go?

599
00:44:41,400 --> 00:44:42,680
Why are you still following me?

600
00:44:45,200 --> 00:44:47,600
You turned off your phone.
I couldn't reach you, so I came here.

601
00:44:50,560 --> 00:44:52,440
I'm this close to succeeding.

602
00:44:54,600 --> 00:44:57,880
I've taken down those rich people
who stepped on us.

603
00:44:58,920 --> 00:44:59,960
Did you see the news?

604
00:45:00,760 --> 00:45:02,040
About Mrs. Mookmanee.

605
00:45:04,920 --> 00:45:06,160
She got arrested.

606
00:45:07,440 --> 00:45:08,920
And next,

607
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:11,400
I'll handle her daughter.

608
00:45:12,200 --> 00:45:14,560
I'm going to use
that arrogant little rich girl

609
00:45:15,240 --> 00:45:17,160
to get revenge on Trai

610
00:45:18,600 --> 00:45:20,560
and deal with Pakbung for you.

611
00:45:22,760 --> 00:45:23,600
You…

612
00:45:24,720 --> 00:45:25,560
What are you going to do?

613
00:45:33,720 --> 00:45:34,880
Just wait and see.

614
00:46:00,240 --> 00:46:02,240
TRAI

615
00:46:19,840 --> 00:46:21,720
Pick up, Trai. Pick up.

616
00:46:25,680 --> 00:46:27,320
DARIN

617
00:46:27,400 --> 00:46:29,080
Trai, have you seen the news?

618
00:46:29,680 --> 00:46:30,520
What?

619
00:46:30,600 --> 00:46:32,360
Someone got Mrs. Mookmanee out.

620
00:46:32,440 --> 00:46:34,160
They said
she's leaving the country tonight.

621
00:46:34,760 --> 00:46:35,600
Wait. How?

622
00:46:35,680 --> 00:46:37,160
I'll get the car ready.

623
00:46:47,040 --> 00:46:48,320
Hello, Da. What is it?

624
00:46:52,560 --> 00:46:54,200
What is Rut going to do to Pakbung?

625
00:46:58,320 --> 00:47:00,520
Kanah, what do you feel like eating?

626
00:47:00,600 --> 00:47:02,480
Uh… the usual place?

627
00:47:02,560 --> 00:47:03,720
Let's grab it before we go home.

628
00:47:04,320 --> 00:47:06,000
- Sure.
- I've been craving it.

629
00:47:07,920 --> 00:47:09,800
- If you want it, let's go.
- Yeah.

630
00:47:09,880 --> 00:47:10,720
And today,

631
00:47:10,800 --> 00:47:13,200
any classes or exams?

632
00:47:13,280 --> 00:47:15,200
Not right now.

633
00:47:15,280 --> 00:47:16,960
- But I've been studying.
- Yeah?

634
00:47:29,360 --> 00:47:30,680
Where'd they go?

635
00:47:38,080 --> 00:47:39,120
What do you want now?

636
00:47:40,120 --> 00:47:41,520
Why are you following us?

637
00:47:45,640 --> 00:47:46,560
I just

638
00:47:47,400 --> 00:47:48,400
happened to be passing by.

639
00:47:49,040 --> 00:47:50,120
Pakbung…

640
00:47:50,960 --> 00:47:51,800
Kanah…

641
00:47:52,560 --> 00:47:54,080
you two are doing well, right?

642
00:47:54,160 --> 00:47:56,240
Except having been lured to get murdered,

643
00:47:57,080 --> 00:47:58,280
then I'm fine.

644
00:47:58,360 --> 00:48:00,960
- Wait. Listen.
- Pakbung told me everything.

645
00:48:01,040 --> 00:48:02,560
How could you do that?

646
00:48:02,640 --> 00:48:04,680
You lured her there
so Mrs. Mookmanee could kill her.

647
00:48:04,760 --> 00:48:06,000
Isn't that too much, Dad?

648
00:48:06,080 --> 00:48:07,960
Wait. Kanah,

649
00:48:08,560 --> 00:48:09,840
Pakbung,

650
00:48:10,480 --> 00:48:11,680
let me explain.

651
00:48:11,760 --> 00:48:13,640
I didn't want to do that.

652
00:48:13,720 --> 00:48:15,160
But…

653
00:48:17,720 --> 00:48:19,360
you told me to go back there,

654
00:48:20,760 --> 00:48:22,160
and

655
00:48:22,240 --> 00:48:23,640
when I went there…

656
00:48:26,240 --> 00:48:27,520
So it's my fault?

657
00:48:28,120 --> 00:48:29,360
Yeah.

658
00:48:29,440 --> 00:48:30,360
I'm the one at fault,

659
00:48:31,040 --> 00:48:32,800
for forcing you,

660
00:48:32,880 --> 00:48:34,800
for testing you.

661
00:48:35,360 --> 00:48:37,640
It's my fault for wanting to know
if you loved me at all

662
00:48:37,720 --> 00:48:39,800
when I already knew the answer.

663
00:48:39,880 --> 00:48:42,280
No. It's not like that, Pakbung.

664
00:48:43,360 --> 00:48:44,840
That's not what I meant.

665
00:48:46,040 --> 00:48:47,040
I was forced.

666
00:48:47,120 --> 00:48:48,920
Mrs. Mookmanee threatened to kill me.

667
00:48:49,000 --> 00:48:50,840
Rut had a gun on me.

668
00:48:51,640 --> 00:48:52,960
I didn't want to do it.

669
00:48:53,040 --> 00:48:53,960
Enough.

670
00:48:54,480 --> 00:48:55,440
That's enough.

671
00:48:55,520 --> 00:48:56,840
I don't want to hear it.

672
00:48:57,440 --> 00:48:59,360
Stop making up lies.

673
00:48:59,440 --> 00:49:01,120
I don't believe you.

674
00:49:01,200 --> 00:49:03,880
But I told you the truth, Pakbung.
I really did.

675
00:49:06,520 --> 00:49:09,000
Kanah, I told the truth. I didn't lie.

676
00:49:10,160 --> 00:49:11,960
Kanah. Kanah.

677
00:49:15,600 --> 00:49:18,000
You're all together now, huh?

678
00:49:20,360 --> 00:49:22,000
Did you trick me again?

679
00:49:33,280 --> 00:49:34,640
Hey! Kanah!

680
00:49:34,720 --> 00:49:36,120
- Kanah.
- Hey!

681
00:49:36,720 --> 00:49:37,880
Kanah!

682
00:49:37,960 --> 00:49:39,720
Kanah. Kanah.

683
00:49:40,320 --> 00:49:42,760
Kanah! Let me go. Kanah!

684
00:49:42,840 --> 00:49:45,000
- Kanah!
- Kanah!

685
00:49:45,080 --> 00:49:46,160
Kanah.

686
00:49:47,800 --> 00:49:49,000
Kanah!

687
00:49:51,680 --> 00:49:52,680
Because of you,

688
00:49:52,760 --> 00:49:53,920
my mother's in prison!

689
00:49:54,000 --> 00:49:56,160
Your mom's evil on her own!

690
00:49:56,240 --> 00:49:57,400
For people like you,

691
00:49:57,480 --> 00:49:58,680
prison's still too good.

692
00:49:59,680 --> 00:50:01,280
So you're not learning at all?!

693
00:50:02,400 --> 00:50:03,760
Hey! What are you doing?!

694
00:50:04,640 --> 00:50:05,800
Don't touch my friend!

695
00:50:06,400 --> 00:50:08,160
Let go!

696
00:50:08,240 --> 00:50:09,920
Hey! Stop!

697
00:50:10,640 --> 00:50:12,240
- Ow!
- Samlee.

698
00:50:12,320 --> 00:50:13,240
Niuniu.

699
00:50:13,320 --> 00:50:14,560
You hurt my friend?

700
00:50:19,280 --> 00:50:21,640
Stop! I'm live streaming right now!

701
00:50:24,600 --> 00:50:25,520
Stop it!

702
00:50:26,040 --> 00:50:27,040
Niuniu!

703
00:50:27,120 --> 00:50:29,160
You bastard! Asshole!

704
00:50:29,240 --> 00:50:30,680
Don't touch my friend!

705
00:50:31,480 --> 00:50:34,920
I will. And I'll kill them
right in front of you.

706
00:50:35,000 --> 00:50:36,080
Do it.

707
00:50:39,120 --> 00:50:41,640
Don't hurt my friends!

708
00:50:43,320 --> 00:50:45,040
Kanah, your inhaler.

709
00:50:45,120 --> 00:50:46,200
Kanah, your inhaler.

710
00:50:47,120 --> 00:50:48,200
Kanah.

711
00:50:48,280 --> 00:50:51,840
You must love your brother so much, right?

712
00:50:52,400 --> 00:50:54,800
Then watch him die in front of you.

713
00:50:55,400 --> 00:50:56,800
- Kanah.
- Mika, you monster!

714
00:50:57,720 --> 00:50:58,680
Let go of him!

715
00:50:58,760 --> 00:51:00,760
Don't touch him! Stay away from him!

716
00:51:02,000 --> 00:51:02,840
Kanah!

717
00:51:04,880 --> 00:51:07,040
Kanah! Mika!

718
00:51:07,120 --> 00:51:08,840
Let him go!

719
00:51:13,000 --> 00:51:14,240
What's wrong?

720
00:51:14,320 --> 00:51:15,640
Are you crying?

721
00:51:17,400 --> 00:51:18,560
Poor thing.

722
00:51:21,240 --> 00:51:23,440
Don't do that to Kanah…

723
00:51:25,040 --> 00:51:26,040
‪Let go of me.

724
00:51:28,680 --> 00:51:29,600
Let go!

725
00:51:29,680 --> 00:51:31,320
Give me my kid's inhaler! Give it back!

726
00:51:34,720 --> 00:51:37,800
Kanah, Kanah, Kanah, hang in there.

727
00:51:38,480 --> 00:51:39,880
Hang in there.

728
00:51:40,880 --> 00:51:42,720
Go deal with him, you idiots! Go!

729
00:51:45,680 --> 00:51:46,760
‪No!

730
00:51:48,440 --> 00:51:49,920
- Dad.
- I'm okay.

731
00:51:50,000 --> 00:51:51,040
I'm okay.

732
00:51:54,920 --> 00:51:56,600
You dared to hurt me?

733
00:52:22,680 --> 00:52:24,480
So, the reason he agreed to help you

734
00:52:24,560 --> 00:52:26,520
is because of your past relationship.

735
00:52:26,600 --> 00:52:29,680
And he also told me to remind you
to keep a very low profile.

736
00:52:29,760 --> 00:52:32,000
If possible, go abroad for a while.

737
00:52:32,080 --> 00:52:33,760
Wait for things to die down,
then come back.

738
00:52:34,400 --> 00:52:35,920
Are you listening to me?

739
00:52:36,000 --> 00:52:37,720
I am.

740
00:52:38,320 --> 00:52:39,280
I get it!

741
00:52:39,360 --> 00:52:41,240
I'm calling my daughter right now.

742
00:52:41,320 --> 00:52:43,440
We're flying to Switzerland tonight.

743
00:52:43,520 --> 00:52:45,960
I promise I won't cause him any trouble.

744
00:52:46,640 --> 00:52:47,480
Happy now?

745
00:52:49,880 --> 00:52:51,680
And why aren't you picking up my call?

746
00:52:57,520 --> 00:52:58,480
Rachen.

747
00:52:59,240 --> 00:53:01,120
You're running off by yourself
and leaving your daughter behind?

748
00:53:02,240 --> 00:53:03,280
Look.

749
00:53:03,360 --> 00:53:06,240
Your daughter is about to become
a murderer in front of the whole world.

750
00:53:19,680 --> 00:53:20,680
Mika.

751
00:53:24,680 --> 00:53:25,640
Bung.

752
00:53:25,720 --> 00:53:27,080
You see it now?

753
00:53:27,680 --> 00:53:29,320
You see what I can do?

754
00:53:29,400 --> 00:53:30,680
Are you scared now?

755
00:53:30,760 --> 00:53:32,240
Are you all scared of dying now?!

756
00:53:33,320 --> 00:53:34,960
Ms. Mika,

757
00:53:35,920 --> 00:53:36,880
I'm scared.

758
00:53:36,960 --> 00:53:39,000
Please don't hurt us.

759
00:53:39,080 --> 00:53:40,880
Please, I'm begging you.

760
00:53:40,960 --> 00:53:44,120
If you hate me,
then just do it to me alone.

761
00:53:48,080 --> 00:53:50,120
And how would that satisfy me?

762
00:53:51,240 --> 00:53:52,960
My mom taught me

763
00:53:53,480 --> 00:53:55,440
that if I hate you,

764
00:53:55,520 --> 00:53:58,080
I have to hurt the people around you too.

765
00:53:58,160 --> 00:53:59,840
That's what revenge is.

766
00:54:03,600 --> 00:54:07,200
You love your brother so much, right?

767
00:54:08,880 --> 00:54:10,360
Then how about you watch him die?

768
00:54:13,480 --> 00:54:15,920
- Kanah.
- Ms. Mika. Ms. Mika.

769
00:54:16,000 --> 00:54:18,280
Ms. Mika.

770
00:54:18,360 --> 00:54:19,920
I'm begging you.

771
00:54:20,000 --> 00:54:22,080
Don't hurt my kid, please.

772
00:54:22,760 --> 00:54:24,360
Then you'll be first.

773
00:54:26,280 --> 00:54:28,080
Dad!

774
00:54:28,160 --> 00:54:29,440
Dad!

775
00:54:31,840 --> 00:54:32,760
Let go!

776
00:54:33,480 --> 00:54:34,680
I'm okay.

777
00:54:39,760 --> 00:54:41,280
Ms. Mika…

778
00:54:42,920 --> 00:54:44,200
Please don't hurt us.

779
00:54:44,280 --> 00:54:46,200
Please let us go.

780
00:54:46,280 --> 00:54:48,760
Please don't kill us.

781
00:54:49,520 --> 00:54:50,920
I'm begging you.

782
00:54:56,280 --> 00:54:58,000
Shut your mouth.

783
00:54:58,640 --> 00:55:00,440
It's because of you. Only you.

784
00:55:00,520 --> 00:55:02,880
Bowing to my feet now is too late.
Do you hear me?

785
00:55:09,800 --> 00:55:11,200
No!

786
00:55:11,960 --> 00:55:13,080
- Dad!
- Dad!

787
00:55:17,120 --> 00:55:18,080
Dad!

788
00:55:19,960 --> 00:55:22,080
- Dad.
- Dad.

789
00:55:22,160 --> 00:55:24,040
I love you,

790
00:55:24,120 --> 00:55:25,240
- Pakbung.
- No!

791
00:55:25,320 --> 00:55:26,880
No! No!

792
00:55:30,160 --> 00:55:33,280
Dad! Dad!

793
00:55:33,360 --> 00:55:35,000
Dad!

794
00:55:35,080 --> 00:55:36,600
Dad!

795
00:55:38,600 --> 00:55:40,320
‪Dad!

796
00:55:41,080 --> 00:55:42,280
‪Dad!

797
00:55:44,920 --> 00:55:45,920
‪Dad!

798
00:55:46,520 --> 00:55:47,400
Dad!

799
00:55:49,640 --> 00:55:50,480
That's enough, Mika.

800
00:55:50,560 --> 00:55:52,280
Do you really want to be a murderer?!

801
00:55:52,920 --> 00:55:53,880
Trai!

802
00:55:56,440 --> 00:55:57,480
- Pakbung.
- Help my dad.

803
00:55:57,560 --> 00:55:59,880
- Help my dad!
- Pakbung.

804
00:56:00,560 --> 00:56:02,400
Please. Dad!

805
00:56:03,280 --> 00:56:04,880
Dad. Help him.

806
00:56:06,400 --> 00:56:07,520
Dad…

807
00:56:07,600 --> 00:56:09,520
- Help him.
- This wasn't how it was supposed to be.

808
00:56:09,600 --> 00:56:11,160
‪It wasn't supposed to be like this.

809
00:56:11,240 --> 00:56:12,520
It wasn't supposed to be like this.

810
00:56:14,640 --> 00:56:16,680
- Dad…
- The police are here.

811
00:56:16,760 --> 00:56:19,040
- No! No!
- Lieutenant!

812
00:56:27,560 --> 00:56:29,640
- Dad.
- Dad.

813
00:56:32,360 --> 00:56:34,200
Mom, where are you?

814
00:56:34,280 --> 00:56:37,280
Mom, help me. Mom…

815
00:56:37,920 --> 00:56:39,400
Mom…

816
00:56:41,880 --> 00:56:43,760
Mom, where are you?

817
00:57:03,600 --> 00:57:04,440
Mika.

818
00:57:06,120 --> 00:57:07,280
Mika!

819
00:57:11,760 --> 00:57:12,840
Mom.

820
00:57:15,800 --> 00:57:16,880
Mom.

821
00:57:38,720 --> 00:57:39,920
Mika!

822
00:57:41,600 --> 00:57:43,560
Kanah, look at me. Kanah.

823
00:57:49,440 --> 00:57:50,960
Don't die, Dad.

824
00:57:51,920 --> 00:57:53,080
Dad.

825
00:57:56,040 --> 00:57:58,200
- Take a deep breath.
- Hang in there.

826
00:57:58,280 --> 00:57:59,640
We're at the hospital now.

827
00:58:01,760 --> 00:58:03,560
Dad, hang in there.

828
00:58:05,480 --> 00:58:06,760
Dad.

829
00:58:14,960 --> 00:58:17,000
Uncle Yongyut's going to be fine.

830
00:58:19,200 --> 00:58:20,280
Stay strong.

831
00:58:25,400 --> 00:58:27,160
<i>Mr. Rut Rueangwichan</i>

832
00:58:27,240 --> 00:58:28,520
<i>is currently on the run.</i>

833
00:58:28,600 --> 00:58:29,840
<i>If you spot him,</i>

834
00:58:29,920 --> 00:58:31,640
<i>I'll reward you immediately in cash,</i>

835
00:58:31,720 --> 00:58:32,840
<i>100,000 baht.</i>

836
00:58:34,240 --> 00:58:36,440
You think your money is God or something?

837
00:58:36,520 --> 00:58:38,440
Our customers'
personal info database got hacked.

838
00:58:38,520 --> 00:58:39,560
He's threatening

839
00:58:39,640 --> 00:58:41,720
to leak customer data bit by bit

840
00:58:41,800 --> 00:58:43,480
if we don't pay him 100 million baht.

841
00:58:43,560 --> 00:58:44,920
100 million?

842
00:58:45,000 --> 00:58:47,440
Your life with Trai will never be peaceful

843
00:58:47,520 --> 00:58:49,440
if you let him get away with it.

844
00:58:49,520 --> 00:58:51,160
Let's work together.

845
00:58:56,600 --> 00:58:57,680
Pakbung.

846
00:59:01,200 --> 00:59:02,920
<i>And then I'll blow you up. Boom!</i>

847
00:59:03,000 --> 00:59:04,800
Both your hearts will merge together.

848
00:59:09,040 --> 00:59:10,280
‪No.

849
00:59:10,360 --> 00:59:11,680
- No…
- Rut, don't.

850
00:59:14,320 --> 00:59:15,320
No!

851
